      "content": "thanks. yeah i checked the null checks in that service and they seem fine. the weird part is that it only happens maybe 5% of the time. the coupon definitely exists in the DB when the user enters it. is there any reason it would just randomly go null in the middle of the request? like a race condition or something?",
